description: List of equivalent(or very similar in the context of Question Answering) relation clusters from multiple popular knowledge bases (DBpedia, Wikidata, Freebase, Tacred)
format: Array of objects. Each object contains a list of property URIs for each available dataset. Relations URIs prefixed by _ symbol imply the subject and object are reversed.

dataset.description: Not available or not existing.

label: movement
